<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The quest for this item is hard because of a rare spawn issue.  You must kill Sentry Alchien, who is in South Karana and runs between the aviak city and stone bridge.  He is either in werewolf form or human form (I know of no one that has seen him as a werewolf).  In his human form he hits for 100's I've been told, and beware of a large faction hit for killing him when he's human, but I'm not sure about when he is a werewolf.</font></td></tr></table>
